{"tid":2448867,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李百全新招閹港台 未製作先審查","createTime":"2021-03-16T08:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T08:54:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1ec113a8301688d90597caa4c6755c857da714c5","tid":2448867,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:31:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210316/VTZCE2J6VJFPJJDTAEGTBQNUZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210316%2FVTZCE2J6VJFPJJDTAEGTBQNUZU%2F&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirEBSGL744lGwoqCHTcH8MN0%3D&h=098622ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210316%2FVTZCE2J6VJFPJJDTAEGTBQNUZU%2F&h=0c59defe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210316/VTZCE2J6VJFPJJDTAEGTBQNUZU/</a><br />\n<br />\n李百全新招閹港台 未製作先審查<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IohxTRvzhzGM_KdPQwRJk74TYXc=/1276x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BXOLE6UAMNDX3NC7NX2PI4YPZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIohxTRvzhzGM_KdPQwRJk74TYXc%3D%2F1276x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBXOLE6UAMNDX3NC7NX2PI4YPZE.jpg&h=81f68c05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣播處長李百全<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】廣播處長李百全（圖）上任後多次自閹，抽起《香港故事》及《議事論事》等多個節目。李昨日出席立法會會議時未有正面回應節目被抽起的原因，但透露上星期引入新機制，要求員工在製作初期以白紙黑字交上建議書，由他和管理團隊審定是否批准，以免要再臨時抽起節目，意味李進一步干涉港台節目的內容。而港台節目製作人員工會要求與李會面，促對方交代抽起節目原因。<br />\n<br />\n立法會資訊事務委員會昨。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工會促會面交代抽節目原因<br />\n<br />\n李百全指上任後，編輯管理將是「重中之重」，而處長作為總編輯及管理團隊，過往角色不夠明顯，揚言以後會扮演好領導角色。他稱約章定明「港台擁有編輯自主」，「並唔係個別節目製作單位（擁有）編輯自主」。若節目不符約章，不會讓節目出街。至於港台有多少員工沒有宣誓，李指絕大部份員工已宣誓。<br />\n<br />\n李強調編輯管理「會揸住宗旨」去做，透露上周引入新機制，要求員工在製。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n商經局長邱騰華指港台節目由製作至播出前均應自行作決定，而非由公眾評論節目應否「出街」，「出唔出街係總編輯嘅責任」。<br />\n<br />\n港台節目製作人員工會昨向李百全發公開信，要求處長與工會會面交代抽起節目的原因。工會指處長檢視《香港故事》相關集數後，認為未能符合《香港電台約章》及《節目製作人。。。。。。"},{"pid":"0041833b768638cfa79d3bb1025b36c25ebda4b2","tid":2448867,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:31:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66893e6d30e0ef80100037ae9bd836e1819b5ff5","tid":2448867,"uid":143241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:34:35.000Z","msg":"你識鬼做製作咩,揸住共產黨嘅宗旨去做就叻,下面無人屌柒佢嘅咩？"},{"pid":"070baaf2f4f68dd5f2e02e7c63ca8475ff822e09","tid":2448867,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:35:39.000Z","msg":"呢條撚樣同鄧忍光一樣都係垃撚圾"},{"pid":"cb4b37d28e437774ced1889f820e128fce882240","tid":2448867,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66893e6d30e0ef80100037ae9bd836e1819b5ff5","tid":2448867,"uid":143241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:34:35.000Z","msg":"你識鬼做製作咩,揸住共產黨嘅宗旨去做就叻,下面無人屌柒佢嘅咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:36:54.000Z","msg":"想無得撈呀，得罪港共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77aa207c08b0df3f9da5bbf3d8e91e8f23b4ad08","tid":2448867,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:44:14.000Z","msg":"交張白紙上去啦<br />\n咁撚勁等佢自已度橋度內容同對白運鏡影音剪接後製<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fa335c78db68315a8b4c3f22bc25c0dc418f3e","tid":2448867,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb4b37d28e437774ced1889f820e128fce882240","tid":2448867,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66893e6d30e0ef80100037ae9bd836e1819b5ff5","tid":2448867,"uid":143241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:34:35.000Z","msg":"你識鬼做製作咩,揸住共產黨嘅宗旨去做就叻,下面無人屌柒佢嘅咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:36:54.000Z","msg":"想無得撈呀，得罪港共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":